longBusinessSummary: Instadose Pharma Corp. operates cultivation, processing, and distribution platforms for cannabis biomass and cannabinoid oil in Canada. It produces active pharmaceutical ingredients for use in pharmaceutical, nutraceutical, and food and beverage companies. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Burlington, Canada.
